bbox": [1106.5, 899.4, 1147.1, 919.2]}, {"text": "December 31, 2017", "bbox": [106.3, 926.5, 253.4, 946.3]}, {"text": "1,063", "bbox": [650.1, 926.5, 690.7, 946.3]}, {"text": "79", "bbox": [824.7, 926.5, 842.8, 946.3]}, {"text": "786", "bbox": [967.9, 926.5, 995.0, 946.3]}, {"text": "1,928", "bbox": [1106.5, 926.5, 1147.1, 946.3]}, {"text": "December 31, 2018 (e)", "bbox": [106.3, 953.6, 269.9, 973.3]}, {"text": "1,202", "bbox": [650.1, 953.6, 690.7, 973.4]}, {"text": "79", "bbox": [824.7, 953.6, 842.8, 973.4]}, {"text": "721", "bbox": [967.9, 953.6, 995.0, 973.4]}, {"text": "2,002", "bbox": [1106.5, 953.6, 1147.1, 973.4]}, {"text": "PROVED UNDEVELOPED RESERVES (f)", "bbox": [81.3, 980.6, 401.6, 1001.5]}, {"text": "December 31, 2015", "bbox": [106.3, 1009.8, 248.9, 1029.6]}, {"text": "321", "bbox": [663.6, 1009.8, 690.7, 1029.6]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [826.6, 1009.8, 859.0, 1029.6]}, {"text": "147", "bbox": [967.9, 1009.8, 1011.2, 1029.6]}, {"text": "468", "bbox": [1120.0, 1009.8, 1147.1, 1029.6]}, {"text": "December 31, 2016", "bbox": [106.3, 1036.9, 248.9, 1056.7]}, {"text": "416", "bbox": [663.6, 1036.9, 690.7, 1056.7]}, {"text": "2", "bbox": [833.8, 1036.9, 859.0, 1056.7]}, {"text": "132", "bbox": [967.9, 1036.9, 1011.2, 1056.7]}, {"text": "550", "bbox": [1120.0, 1036.9, 1147.1, 1056.7]}, {"text": "December 31, 2017", "bbox": [106.3, 1064.0, 253.4, 1083.8]}, {"text": "492", "bbox": [663.6, 1064.0, 690.7, 1083.8]}, {"text": "5", "bbox": [833.8, 1064.0, 859.0, 1083.8]}, {"text": "173", "bbox": [967.9, 1064.0, 1011.2, 1083.8]}, {"text": "670", "bbox": [1120.0, 1064.0, 1147.1, 1083.8]}, {"text": "December 31, 2018", "bbox": [106.3, 1091.1, 257.0, 1110.9]}, {"text": "509", "bbox": [663.6, 1091.1, 690.7, 1110.9]}, {"text": "19", "bbox": [824.7, 1091.1, 842.8, 1110.9]}, {"text": "222", "bbox": [967.9, 1091.1, 995.0, 1110.9]}, {"text": "750", "bbox": [1120.0, 1091.1, 1147.1, 1110.9]}, {"text": "(a)", "bbox": [75.0, 1120.4, 96.8, 1138.1]}, {"text": "Natural gas volumes have been converted to barrels of oil equivalent (BOE) based on energy content of six thousand cubic feet (Mcf) of gas to one barrel of oil.", "bbox": [112.6, 1120.4, 1157.6, 1138.1]}, {"text": "Barrels of oil equivalence does not necessarily result in price equivalence. The price of natural gas on a barrel of oil equivalent basis is currently substantially lower", "bbox": [112.6, 1141.7, 1157.6, 1159.4]}, {"text": "than the corresponding price for oil and has been similarly lower for a number of years. For example, in 2018, the average daily prices of West Texas Intermediate", "bbox": [112.6, 1162.9, 1157.6, 1180.6]}, {"text": "(WTI) oil and New York Mercantile Exchange (NYMEX) natural gas were $64.77 per barrel and $2.97 per Mcf, respectively, resulting in an oil to gas ratio of over 20", "bbox": [112.6, 1184.2, 1157.7, 1201.9]}, {"text": "to 1.", "bbox": [112.6, 1205.4, 140.8, 1223.1]}, {"text": "(b)", "bbox": [75.0, 1226.7, 96.8, 1244.4]}, {"text": "Included proved reserves related to PSCs and other similar economic arrangements of 0.3 billion BOE, 0.5 billion BOE, 0.5 billion BOE, and 0.5 billion BOE at", "bbox": [112.5, 1226.7, 1157.7, 1244.4]}, {"text": "December 31, 2018, 2017, 2016 and 2015, respectively.", "bbox": [112.6, 1247.9, 473.3, 1265.7]}, {"text": "(c)", "bbox": [75.0, 1269.2, 96.0, 1286.9]}, {"text": "Revisions of previous estimates in 2018 primarily reflected positive revisions in Permian Basin related to prices and Al Hosn Gas due to improved performance.", "bbox": [112.5, 1269.2, 1157.6, 1286.9]}, {"text": "Revisions of previous estimates in 2017 reflected positive revisions in the Permian Basin and Oman. Revisions in 2016 are primarily positive revisions in Al Hosn", "bbox": [112.6, 1290.5, 1157.6, 1308.2]}, {"text": "Gas and price revisions in Oman due to the PSC impact, partially offset by negative domestic price revisions.", "bbox": [112.6, 1311.7, 815.7, 1329.4]}, {"text": "(d)", "bbox": [75.0, 1333.0, 96.8, 1350.7]}, {"text": "Sales of proved reserves in 2018 were primarily related to the sale of non-core acreage in the Permian Basin. Sales of proved reserves in 2017 were primarily related", "bbox": [112.5, 1333.0, 1157.7, 1350.7]}, {"text": "to the sale of South Texas and non-core acreage in the Permian Basin. 2016 sales of proved reserves are related to Libya and Piceance.", "bbox": [112.5, 1354.2, 995.0, 1371.9]}, {"text": "(e)", "bbox": [75.0, 1375.5, 96.8, 1393.2]}, {"text": "Approximately 9 percent of the proved developed reserves at December 31, 2018, are nonproducing, primarily associated with Oman and Permian EOR.", "bbox": [112.5, 1375.5, 1093.8, 1393.2]}, {"text": "(f)", "bbox": [75.0, 1396.7, 92.8, 1414.5]}, {"text": "Proved undeveloped reserves in the Permian Basin are supported by a five-year detailed field-level development plan, which includes the timing, location and capital", "bbox": [112.5, 1396.7, 1157.6, 1414.5]}, {"text": "commitment of the wells to be drilled. Only proved undeveloped reserves which are reasonably certain to be drilled within five years of booking and are supported", "bbox": [112.5, 1418.0, 1157.7, 1435.7]}, {"text": "by a final investment decision to drill them are included in the development plan. A portion of the proved undeveloped reserves associated with international operations", "bbox": [112.5, 1439.3, 1157.6, 1457.0]}, {"text": "are expected to be developed beyond the five years and are tied to approved long-term development plans.", "bbox": [112.5, 1460.5, 807.2, 1478.2]}, {"text": "Q", "bbox": [527.8, 3.9, 557.5, 41.9]}]}